  "_comment": "Per-writing-system letter tables for the LLM-free intro 'learn the script' course. Keyed by SCRIPT (many languages share one); _langScript maps a language code to its script(s). Every language must be mapped: an unmapped code reads as 'no script', which wrongly makes a Latin course look teachable to its speakers.",
